{"tid":2095371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透幻愛]大家覺得志樂同返欣欣一齊定葉嵐一齊","createTime":"2020-07-05T11:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T11:55:32.000Z","uid":66582,"like":25,"dislike":119,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8fac1c831989503cf1c49665cee4c4366a57a521","tid":2095371,"uid":66582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"未睇幻愛嘅可以出返去，真心推介，一定要去睇支持吓香港本地電影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實本身好憎葉嵐，但睇睇吓又覺得佢好可憐，<br />\n感覺有少少you know my name, not my story<br />\n有時有好多嘢即係得自己先知同明白。<br />\n<br />\n最後嗰幕雖然我好希望志樂係同返葉嵐一齊，<br />\n但感覺上覺得嗰個應該係欣欣，唔知大家又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同返欣欣一齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同返葉嵐一齊"},{"pid":"b0d4e3c3d533ecbcc72aa8459d71e9a60d0ad7b3","tid":2095371,"uid":66582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"333404a4897eb2771d457290470e8d90435e47d1","tid":2095371,"uid":66582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:38:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"516e69c3a84e01a5f7d48be5c9ec8c6d8eddc0c4","tid":2095371,"uid":66582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f3543fa256580ad66d42e54a6ee0fac83630579","tid":2095371,"uid":66582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e58db404071d6a541671d984e7ff97e276321f9","tid":2095371,"uid":115579,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:40:39.000Z","msg":"我先係真㗎屌你"},{"pid":"3e2890c61977058f2a70d00fc3f5d562489335f0","tid":2095371,"uid":66582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:41:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"150198